<li id="cite_note-9"><b><a href="#cite_ref-9" title="">^</a></b> âHerrshaftszeichen eines wodanistisches KÃ¶nigtumsâ, <i>Jahrbuch fur frankische Landesforschung</i> 14 (1966), pp. 9-66.</li>
<li id="cite_note-10"><b><a href="#cite_ref-10" title="">^</a></b> 101-102, âKingship Rituals and Ideology in Lombard Italyâ 95-114, <i>Rituals of Power From Late Antiquity to the Early Middle Ages.</i> ed. by Frans Theuws &amp; Janet L. Nelson, (Leiden: Brill, 2000)</li>
<li id="cite_note-11"><b><a href="#cite_ref-11" title="">^</a></b> <i>Historia Langobardorum</i> VI, 55</li>
<li id="cite_note-12"><b><a href="#cite_ref-12" title="">^</a></b> <cite style="font-style:normal" class="book" id="CITEREFRavenscroft1982">Ravenscroft, Trevor (1982). <i>The Spear of Destiny</i>. Weiser Books. <a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/0877285470" class="internal">ISBN 0877285470</a>.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.btitle=The+Spear+of+Destiny&amp;rft.aulast=Ravenscroft&amp;rft.aufirst=Trevor&amp;rft.au=Ravenscroft%2C+Trevor&amp;rft.date=1982&amp;rft.pub=Weiser+Books&amp;rft.isbn=0877285470&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Holy_Lance"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
<li id="cite_note-13"><b><a href="#cite_ref-13" title="">^</a></b> <cite style="font-style:normal" class="book" id="CITEREFRavenscroftTim_Wallace-Murphy">Ravenscroft, Trevor; Tim Wallace-Murphy (1997 (reprint)). <i>The Mark of the Beast: The Continuing Story of the Spear of Destiny</i>. Weiser Books. <a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/0877288704" class="internal">ISBN 0877288704</a>.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.btitle=The+Mark+of+the+Beast%3A+The+Continuing+Story+of+the+Spear+of+Destiny&amp;rft.aulast=Ravenscroft&amp;rft.aufirst=Trevor&amp;rft.au=Ravenscroft%2C+Trevor&amp;rft.au=Tim+Wallace-Murphy&amp;rft.date=1997+%28reprint%29&amp;rft.pub=Weiser+Books&amp;rft.isbn=0877288704&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Holy_Lance"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
<li id="cite_note-14"><b><a href="#cite_ref-14" title="">^</a></b> <a href="http://slcc.strath.ac.uk/scotslawcourse/ip/ip/copy/raven.html" class="external text" title="http://slcc.strath.ac.uk/scotslawcourse/ip/ip/copy/raven.html" rel="nofollow">Ravenscroft v Herbert [1980</a> RPC 193]</li>
<li id="cite_note-15"><b><a href="#cite_ref-15" title="">^</a></b> <cite style="font-style:normal" class="news" id="CITEREFMark_Rice-Oxley2006">Mark Rice-Oxley (2006-03-06). <a href="http://www.csmonitor.com/2006/0306/p01s01-woeu.html?s=widep" class="external text" title="http://www.csmonitor.com/2006/0306/p01s01-woeu.html?s=widep" rel="nofollow">"Did 'Da Vinci Code' Break British Copyright Code?"</a>. Christian Science Monitor<span class="printonly">. <a href="http://www.csmonitor.com/2006/0306/p01s01-woeu.html?s=widep" class="external free" title="http://www.csmonitor.com/2006/0306/p01s01-woeu.html?s=widep" rel="nofollow">http://www.csmonitor.com/2006/0306/p01s01-woeu.html?s=widep</a></span><span class="reference-accessdate">. Retrieved on 2008-02-24</span>.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=bookitem&amp;rft.btitle=Did+%27Da+Vinci+Code%27+Break+British+Copyright+Code%3F&amp;rft.atitle=&amp;rft.aulast=Mark+Rice-Oxley&amp;rft.au=Mark+Rice-Oxley&amp;rft.date=2006-03-06&amp;rft.pub=Christian+Science+Monitor&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.csmonitor.com%2F2006%2F0306%2Fp01s01-woeu.html%3Fs%3Dwidep&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Holy_Lance"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
